_json.description: Rabbit Stew--Rabbit Stew-   3.3 pounds rabbit     1 cup olive oil divided     5 ½ pounds baby onions          3 bay leaves     10 pieces whole peppercorn     6 pieces whole allspice     4 garlic cloves    Marinade      ½ cup olive oil     1 cup red wine     2 tablespoons vinegar     3 bayleaves     10 pieces whole peppercorn     5 pieces whole allspice     4 garlic cloves  Preparation:  Wash the rabbit well and douse with the vinegar.  In large bowl make the marinade and add the rabbit making sure to coat all of the pieces.  Cover well and refrigerate for 24-48 hours
